<font color="#FF0000">JARHEAD CHEER!</font><br>
<tt>Fri Dec 19 22:33:02 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Cookie and a bunch of his Jarhead friends came by my house to sing Christmas Carols....<br><br>
I kept hearing them bellowing away, &quot;Leon Leon Leon..!&quot;<br><br>
Being and Army Officer and a Gentleman..I went down stairs and politely informed them that they were holding their hymnals upside down!<br><br>
Mustang Two Four
